<section id="imagen_index">
    <h1>About Us</h1>
</section>
<div class="container_conocenos">
    <div class="hero-conocenos">
        <div class="texto-principal">
            <p>
                <strong>We are a company committed to sustainability and sports.</strong>
                We have created an application that connects volunteers with sports events, allowing them to participate and collaborate to make each event a greener, more responsible, and socially conscious experience.
            </p>
            <p>
                Our goal is to promote volunteering in the sports sector, fostering teamwork, environmental respect, and social awareness in every activity.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section: Our History -->
    <div class="seccion-historia">
        <h2>Our History</h2>
        <p>
            Voluntariado Verde was born in <strong>2025</strong> thanks to a group of athletes and environmental activists who shared the same vision: to transform sports events into engines of positive change for our planet. What began as a small local initiative in <em>Bilbao</em> has now become a network of over <strong>5,000</strong> active volunteers across <em>Spain</em>.
        </p>
        <p>
            Every year we collaborate in more than <strong>200</strong> sports events, from marathons and triathlons to surfing and mountain biking competitions, ensuring that each event leaves a positive mark on the environment and local communities.
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Section: Mission, Vision, and Values -->
    <div class="tarjetas-mision">
        <div class="tarjeta tarjeta-mision">
            <h3>Our Mission</h3>
            <p>
                Facilitate the connection between committed volunteers and sports event organizers, promoting sustainable practices that minimize environmental impact and maximize social benefit.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="tarjeta tarjeta-vision">
            <h3>Our Vision</h3>
            <p>
                To be a European benchmark in organizing sustainable sports volunteering, inspiring millions of people to combine their passion for sports with caring for the planet.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="tarjeta tarjeta-valores">
            <h3>Our Values</h3>
            <p>
                Environmental commitment, teamwork, social inclusion, transparency, continuous innovation, and respect for all people and communities we collaborate with.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section: Why Join Us -->
    <div class="seccion-unirse">
        <h2>Why join Voluntariado Verde?</h2>
        <ul class="lista-beneficios">
            <li><strong>Unique experience:</strong> Experience sports events from the inside, with privileged access and unforgettable moments.</li>
            <li><strong>Continuous training:</strong> We offer free courses on sustainability, first aid, and event management.</li>
            <li><strong>Active community:</strong> Be part of a network of people committed to sports and the environment.</li>
            <li><strong>Certifications:</strong> Obtain recognized volunteer certificates that enhance your resume.</li>
            <li><strong>Real impact:</strong> Every action counts. Contribute directly to making sports a more sustainable activity.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

</div>
